paragraph1: We know that it can be difficult to find out how everything works - what, when and where to do? We are students from Czech and Slovak bilingual high schools and now we are studying at Spanish universities, we have already gone through the process (and yes, we had DUDAS, MUCHAS DUDAS)
paragraph2: If you have any question, you can contact one of us personally, join the WhatsApp group about studying in Spain or leave your question right here and we will try to answer you as soon as possible to your mail:
degree1: Computer science engineering and business administration and management
todo1: Find out what degrees you are interested in
todo2: Find out which universities offer these degrees
todo3: Find out what are the admission requirements at these universities
useful-paragraph: Sem dáme užitečné informace, všechno co je potřeba udělat, vybrat, atd.
contact-paragraph: Sem dame odkaz na skupinu, muzeme vytvorit treba email nebo neco takoveho, dat jedno tel cislo, i kdyz kontakt na nas uz je na jine casi stranky
faq-paragraph: Sem dame nejake otazky a odpovedi
